  <brief_title>Effect of a Multi-directional Power Toothbrush on Recession</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of a Multi-directional Power and a Manual Toothbrush in Subjects Susceptible to Gingival Recession: A 12-month Randomized Controlled Clinical Study</official_title>
